name: RentMYinstrument.com
tag_list: instrument-rental, online-instruments, rent-instruments, rent-an-instrument, middle-school-bands, band-director-approved, online-merchant
overview:
RentMYinstrument.com provides band director approved, quality band and orchestra musical instrument rental to students, musicians, parents, and music stores.

RentMYinstrument.com was created to bring the instrument rental industry up to speed with the available technologies such as the web. Rather than being tied to just one store or a few brick and mortar locations, rentMYinstrument is everywhere. Free shipping is provided to the 48 continental United States. Over 600 band directors have entered their preferences into the site, making it easy for parents and students to shop at home for the right brand, and right instrument. Instead of just getting “an instrument” with the risk of questionable quality, rentMYinstrument.com provides only new or like new instruments. RentMYinstrument.com also provides solutions to music stores who wish to provide instrument rental but do not have the inventory space. Simple QR window decals enable music stores to advertise their website powered with the instrument selection of www.rentmyinstrument.com Rent to own options are available, flexible terms, ability to change instruments at anytime, and other features and efficiencies demonstrate that rentMYinstrument.com was designed by Music Veterans with Band Directors, Students, Parents, and Music stores in mind.
